Complete UC4 → Payment Flow (now working)
MyBookings (/my-bookings)
    │
    ▼ "View Details →"
BookingDetail (/booking/:id)
    │  GET /bookings/{id}  →  booking has status=PENDING_PAYMENT
    │
    ▼ "💳 Complete Payment" button
    │  Builds flightFromBooking { airline, flightNumber, ... } from booking fields
    │
PaymentPage (/payment)
    │  ✅ booking exists  ✅ flight exists  → page renders correctly
    │  Shows: booking reference, airline, route, passengers, total
    │  User picks payment method → clicks Pay
    │
    ▼ POST /payments/initiate
    │
BookingConfirmation (/booking-confirmation)
    │  ✅ payment + booking + flight all passed in state
    │  Shows: success banner, booking ref, flight details, payment summary
    │
    ▼ "📋 My Bookings" → booking now shows CONFIRMED